{"type":"article","id":14624,"title":"台灣和四川地震，哭笑不得","uid":29574,"topics":[6137,5419],"contents":"我感覺粉蛆的嘴有毒，嘲笑別人的事總會應驗到自己身上。<br>\n<br>\n嘲笑香港豬肉漲價，沒幾天中國人都吃不起豬肉了。嘲笑美國有鼠疫，沒幾天中國也發現鼠疫了。嘲笑丹麥有禽流感，沒幾天中國也有了。。。昨晚台灣地震，他們幸災樂禍，嘴巴都很毒，結果幾個小時後四川也地震了。<br>\n<br>\n還是總加速師說的對：「這都是要應驗的！」<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/ugc0jtt.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/ugc0jtt.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/ugc0jtt.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/g6pgamW.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/g6pgamW.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/g6pgamW.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/JbT2CJC.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/JbT2CJC.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/JbT2CJC.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\na","date":"2020-02-15","agreeCount":10,"discussionCount":0}